Package com.timebuddy.services

package com.timebuddy.services
This package contains service classes that implement the business logic of the application. Services interact with the repositories to perform data operations and apply business rules. Services act as an intermediary between the controller and the repository layers. They are responsible for orchestrating the application's use cases and ensuring data integrity and consistency.
